Package: WatershedTools
Title: Tools for watershed analysis
Version: 1.7.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Matthew",
           family = "Talluto",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "mtalluto@gmail.com")
Description: This is a companion to the watershed package, focused on topological analysis. The main difference is that the watershed package depends on GRASS GIS to delineate the streams. This package performs analyses on the output of watershed, without any dependence on GRASS.
License: MIT + file "Licence"
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
